        public boolean runGoapAction(IGoapUnit goapUnit)
                      throws java.lang.Exception
        Cycle trough all actions until an invalid one or the end of the Queue is reached. A false return type here causes the FSM to pop the state from its stack.
        Specified by:
        runGoapAction in interface IFSMState
        Parameters:
